            "answer": "<p>Most blemish removal treatments are £75 per session, regardless of the type or size of the blemish. This covers skin tags, moles, milia, thread veins, age spots, seborrheic warts, cherry angiomas, warts, xanthelasma, and spider naevi. Multiple blemishes treated in one session are charged per blemish.</p>"
